      <title>Arc 11 Password Locked</title>
      <link>https://shikarito.wordpress.com/2025/01/20/arc-11-password-locked/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://shikarito.wordpress.com/2025/01/20/arc-11-password-locked/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 03:41:50 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;main class="wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"&gt; &lt;div class="wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"&gt;&lt;h1 class="wp-block-post-title"&gt;Arc 11 Password&amp;nbsp;Locked&lt;/h1&gt;  &lt;div style="font-style:italic;font-weight:400;" class="wp-block-post-date has-small-font-size"&gt;&lt;time datetime="2025-01-20T14:41:50+11:00"&gt;&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/2025/01/20/arc-11-password-locked/"&gt;January 20th, 2025&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/time&gt;&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;   &lt;div class="entry-content wp-block-post-content is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained"&gt; &lt;p&gt;A bit delayed since LN13 has been out for a while now, but arc 11 is now hidden behind a password. As usual, the password is in the same place as the arc 10 password.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;I should also mention that 11.10 has the most views out of all the chapters on this blog. As of today, it has 51k views, when the other chapters get an average of 15k views&amp;#8230; is it the power of frog?&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Also, unrelated, I have a sniping/stealing situation with the Kusuriya GX manga scanlation. As some of you probably know, I am translating the manga under the NGS group, but the new group (one person) stole our raws, cleans, and translations and is releasing it as his own. Anyone have any idea what I should do? &lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div id="jp-post-flair" class="sharedaddy sd-like-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-official sd-sharing"&gt;&lt;h3 class="sd-title"&gt;Share this:&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="sd-content"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="share-facebook"&gt;&lt;div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/2025/01/20/arc-11-password-locked/" data-layout="button_count"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="share-end"&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-130534757-5289-67a2e65e0a479' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/index.html?ver=20250205#blog_id=130534757&amp;amp;post_id=5289&amp;amp;origin=shikarito.wordpress.com&amp;amp;obj_id=130534757-5289-67a2e65e0a479' data-name='like-post-frame-130534757-5289-67a2e65e0a479' data-title='Like or Reblog'&gt;&lt;div class='likes-widget-placeholder post-likes-widget-placeholder' style='height: 55px;'&gt;&lt;span class='button'&gt;&lt;span&gt;Like&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class='loading'&gt;Loading&amp;#8230;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class='sd-text-color'&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class='sd-link-color' href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/2025/01/20/arc-11-password-locked/"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;div style="height:32px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;    &lt;div class="wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"&gt; &lt;div class="wp-block-group is-layout-flex wp-block-group-is-layout-flex"&gt;&lt;div style="font-style:italic;font-weight:400;" class="wp-block-post-date has-small-font-size"&gt;&lt;time datetime="2025-01-20T14:41:50+11:00"&gt;January 20, 2025&lt;/time&gt;&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;div class="wp-block-post-author has-small-font-size"&gt;&lt;div class="wp-block-post-author__content"&gt;&lt;p class="wp-block-post-author__name"&gt;AuriCa&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;div class="taxonomy-category wp-block-post-terms has-small-font-size"&gt;&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="tag"&gt;Uncategorized&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;div style="height:32px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;    &lt;hr class="wp-block-separator is-style-wide"/&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-post-comments"&gt; &lt;!-- You can start editing here. --&gt